show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/2ZprTq
show.description:
A billionaire in disguise sacrifices his identity for love—only to be betrayed by the one he trusted most.
Bound by fate in a contract marriage with a powerful woman, he finds himself torn between revenge and desire.
The Ultimate Boss is a storm of secrets, ambition, and unexpected passion where power and love collide.
